@model ElSheemyCoaching.Core.DTOs.AdminCustomerDetailsViewModel
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Localization
@using ElSheemyCoaching.Core.Enums
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "تفاصيل العميل - " + Model.FullName;
    var requestCulture = Context.Features.Get<IRequestCultureFeature>();
    var isArabic = requestCulture?.RequestCulture.Culture.Name.StartsWith("ar") ?? true;
}

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <div class="mb-8 border-b border-white/5 pb-6">
        <a href="@Url.Action("Customers", "Admin")" class="text-dark-400 hover:text-white text-sm flex items-center gap-1 mb-4 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 @(isArabic ? "rotate-180" : "")" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
            </svg>
            @(isArabic ? "العودة لقائمة العملاء" : "Back to Customers")
        </a>
        
        <!-- Profile Header -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 mt-6">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-600 to-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold text-white shadow-xl shadow-brand-500/20 shrink-0">
                @Model.FullName.Substring(0, 1).ToUpper()
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">@Model.FullName</h1>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm text-dark-400">
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-800">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
                        @Model.Email
                    </span>
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-dark-800 font-mono">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
                        @(string.IsNullOrEmpty(Model.PhoneNumber) ? "—" : Model.PhoneNumber)
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-10">
        <div class="bg-dark-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-dark-400 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">@(isArabic ? "الواردات من العميل" : "Total Revenue")</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-brand-400">@Model.TotalSpent.ToString("N0") <span class="text-xs">@(isArabic ? "ج.م" : "EGP")</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-dark-400 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">@(isArabic ? "إجمالي الطلبات" : "Total Orders")</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-white">@Model.OrderCount</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-dark-400 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">@(isArabic ? "طلبات مدفوعة" : "Paid Orders")</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-emerald-400">@Model.Orders.Count(o => o.Status == OrderStatus.Paid)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="text-dark-400 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">@(isArabic ? "متوسط الطلب" : "Avg Order Value")</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold font-mono text-white">
                @(Model.OrderCount > 0 ? (Model.TotalSpent / Model.OrderCount).ToString("N0") : "0") <span class="text-xs">@(isArabic ? "ج.م" : "EGP")</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Order History -->
    <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6">@(isArabic ? "سجل الطلبات" : "Order History")</h2>
        
        @if (Model.Orders.Any())
        {
            <div class="bg-dark-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                <table class="w-full">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="border-b border-white/5 text-dark-500 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-start font-medium">@(isArabic ? "رقم الطلب" : "Order #")</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-start font-medium">@(isArabic ? "التاريخ" : "Date")</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-start font-medium">@(isArabic ? "البرامج" : "Programs")</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-start font-medium">@(isArabic ? "المبلغ" : "Amount")</th>
                            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-start font-medium">@(isArabic ? "الحالة" : "Status")</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="text-sm">
                        @foreach (var order in Model.Orders)
                        {
                            <tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-mono font-medium text-white">@order.OrderNumber</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-dark-400">@order.CreatedAt.ToString("MMM dd, yyyy")</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
                                        @foreach (var item in order.Items)
                                        {
                                            <span class="text-dark-300">@item</span>
                                        }
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 font-mono font-bold text-white">@order.Total.ToString("N0")</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    @if (order.Status == OrderStatus.Paid)
                                    {
                                        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 text-xs font-medium border border-emerald-500/20">
                                            @(isArabic ? "مدفوع" : "Paid")
                                        </span>
                                    }
                                    else if (order.Status == OrderStatus.Cancelled)
                                    {
                                        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 text-xs font-medium border border-red-500/20">
                                            @(isArabic ? "ملغي" : "Cancelled")
                                        </span>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs font-medium border border-amber-500/20">
                                            @(isArabic ? "قيد المراجعة" : "Pending")
                                        </span>
                                    }
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        }
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        }
        else
        {
            <div class="bg-dark-900/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-10 text-center">
                <p class="text-dark-500">@(isArabic ? "لا توجد طلبات لهذا العميل" : "No orders for this customer")</p>
            </div>
        }
    </div>
</section>
